+// SPDX-License-Identifier: GPL-2.0+
+/*
+ * Copyright (C) 2019-2024 Linaro Ltd
+ * Author: Sumit Semwal <sumit.semwal@linaro.org>
+ *	 Dmitry Baryshkov <dmitry.baryshkov@linaro.org>
